flowchart TD
    SP[SharePoint Online<br/>HR staff upload forms<br/>and supporting documents]

    subgraph PROCESS[Automated Validation Pipeline]
        DETECT[Detect new submissions]
        READ[Read and extract<br/>document text]
        CLASSIFY[Identify form type<br/>and supporting documents]
        VALIDATE[Validate documents<br/>against business rules]
    end

    subgraph AZURE[Azure Services]
        FUNC[Azure Functions<br/>Orchestration and processing]
        DI[Azure Document Intelligence<br/>Read and extract document text]
        AOAI[Azure OpenAI<br/>Classify documents and<br/>check business rules]
        SB[Azure Service Bus<br/>Workload buffering]
        BLOB[Azure Storage<br/>Runtime state]
    end

    OUT[SharePoint Results<br/>Status report by form type]

    SP -->|New submission| DETECT
    DETECT --> READ
    READ --> CLASSIFY
    CLASSIFY --> VALIDATE
    VALIDATE --> OUT
    OUT -->|Available to HR staff| SP

    DETECT --- FUNC
    DETECT --- SB
    READ --- DI
    CLASSIFY --- AOAI
    VALIDATE --- AOAI
    FUNC --- BLOB
